div.h3: Check us out on Social Media!

div.span: Norse Force apparel will be available again this year. Each of the school offices have samples of the shirts and order forms. The short and long sleeve t-shirts along with the hooded and crew neck sweatshirts are available as they have been in the past. New this year are the moisture wicking short and long sleeve shirts. Checks for the apparel should be made out the Westby Gymnastics and must be turned in to the office by September 16th. These shirts make great gifts, so if you want to order for a birthday surprise or for Christmas, please mark on the sheet so the shirts are not given to your student. Any profits from the sale of these shirts will be split between the gymnastics team and the American Cancer Society through the Soleburner in Chaseburg. If you have any questions, please contact Tammy Gilkes or Kay Bluske
